description:
Anatomy for acupuncture - Notes and info

This torrent has five files/folders

1. Notes and info.nfo -> This very file, where you are reading. This gives you notes about installation.

2. anatomy for acupuncture_jewel_box.jpg -> Cover picture of Jewel box. Print it and paste it on your Jewel Box.

3. anatomy for acupuncture_CD.jpg -> DVD picture. Print it and paste it on your DVD that you burn.

4. anatomy_for_acupuncture.nrg -> This is the main file. This is the image file of the main DVD. Burn it on a DVD using any DVD burning program like Nero or Alcohol 120%.

5. patch -> This folder contains a file called "setup.exe". Use THIS FILE to install the program. DO NOT INSTAL THE PROGRAM FROM THE DVD THAT YOU BURNT! If you do so, it will ask you for the original DVD.

Now run the program and enjoy!!

And do not forget to leave a note of thanks. This is my only reward.

May God bless you all!!
